# Pillar3Zeta Module

Main entry point for PILAR 3: FUNCIÓN ZETA

This module provides the zeta function theory for the Riemann Hypothesis proof.

## Files

- `zeta_definition.lean`: Definition of ζ(s)
- `analytic_cont.lean`: Analytic continuation
- `functional_eq.lean`: Functional equation
- `zero_classification.lean`: Classification of zeros
